				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/C%E1%BA%A3nh-b%C3%A1o-Th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BA%A5t-nguy%E1%BB%87t-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BB%8B-nh%E1%BA%ADt/poem-R6UhyHNkNFGdxXyw4CHMxQ">Cảnh báo (Thập nhất nguyệt thập nhị nhật) - 警報（十一月十二日）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/author-a7YEflJr1_rcFKC9dgECgQ">Hồ Chí Minh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Anh/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-Qu%E1%BA%A7n-ng%C6%B0-tri%E1%BB%81u-l%C3%BD-%C4%91%E1%BB%93/poem-p_OnqEhO0wCOdBROF6KUrw">Đề “Quần ngư triều lý” đồ - 題群魚朝鯉圖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Anh/author-lYMSgB5b1VLUWjgJGL6J2A">Chu Đường Anh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-T%E1%BA%AFc/%C4%90%E1%BB%93-ch%C3%AD-ca/poem--A3qpFL2UYH8DOEkrBgXVg">Đồ chí ca - 圖誌歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-T%E1%BA%AFc/author-SdALrlg8daTfB8oNiho-Nw">Lê Tắc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/Ph%C3%BA-B%C3%ACnh-thi%E1%BA%BFu-h%E1%BA%A7u/poem-0rtrq4OjsZ2E4DNpZ4faGw">Phú Bình thiếu hầu - 富平少侯</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/Th%C3%B4n-c%C6%B0-th%C6%B0-h%E1%BB%89/poem-s2Qpp_xy27CeUpkbwrxH0Q">Thôn cư thư hỉ - 村居書喜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/Th%C6%B0-s%C3%A0o-k%C3%BD/poem-so9_x8JRDS-uH2_aEO4INA">Thư sào ký - 書巢記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/Th%C6%B0-t%E1%BA%B7ng-Thi%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%B4-am-Minh-Vi%E1%BB%85n-l%C3%A3o-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/poem-GpbDyGl-byWRGN6lWwhXSA">Thư tặng Thiên Đô am Minh Viễn lão thiền sư - 書贈天都庵明遠老禪師</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/author-il2-xU_Q-nIFla-ypApHCA">Trịnh Hoài Đức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/T%C3%ADch-hoa-b%E1%BB%99-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ch%C3%A2u-T%C3%A0ng-Xu%C3%A2n-vi%C3%AAn-ch%E1%BB%A7-nh%C3%A2n-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-bUAdypQNXUXEipKq--T1lg">Tích hoa bộ Tương Châu Tàng Xuân viên chủ nhân nguyên vận kỳ 3 - 惜花步藏湘州春園主人元韻其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/author-TXAaCmjdRWIV6MkCYE1psQ">Lỗ Tấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%E1%BB%89nh-Khi%C3%AAm/T%E1%BB%91ng-l%C3%A3o-thi%E1%BA%BFp-ho%C3%A0n-th%C3%B4n-c%C6%B0/poem-S8-cJZbqJNh14phrpTrhtg">Tống lão thiếp hoàn thôn cư - 送老妾還村居</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%E1%BB%89nh-Khi%C3%AAm/author-Rv6locqJPIunovJpeqDNxA">Nguyễn Bỉnh Khiêm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-S%C6%B0-H%E1%BB%B1u/Tranh-nghinh-k%E1%BB%B3-l%C3%A3o/poem-NwIgEiGckyB8jsxKN30n4A">Tranh nghinh kỳ lão - 爭迎耆老</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-S%C6%B0-H%E1%BB%B1u/author-PX1pV4cjfZZCiPiOoAmgRg">Nguyễn Sư Hựu</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
